# 操作系统文件 (OS Files)
# ========================
.DS_Store           # macOS
Thumbs.db           # Windows
Desktop.ini

# ========================
# 日志文件 (Logs)
# ========================
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ========================
